'''冰山'''（{{lang-en|Iceberg}}）是一块大若山川的[[冰|冰]]，脱离了陸上的[[冰川|冰川]]或[[冰架|冰架]]，並漂浮在廣闊的水面上。<ref>[http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&q=define%3Aiceberg&btnG=Google+Search Numerous definitions of the word "Iceberg"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&q=define%3Aiceberg&btnG=Google+Search |date=20150924163815 }} URL accessed December 20, 2006.</ref>由於冰山質地結實堅硬、體積大，與船擦撞時常導致船難，其中較著名的有1912年所發生的[[泰坦尼克号|泰坦尼克号]]（{{lang|en|RMS Titanic}}）船難。

由於冰山容易造成海上作業的危險，目前已經組成{{tsl|en|International Ice Patrol|國際冰山巡邏隊}}來監測世界冰山的動向，各國也有相關的監測系統。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Iceberg Towing Experiments in the Barents and Kara Seas in 2016–2017|url=https://doi.org/10.17736/ijope.2019.jc768|last=Kornishin|first=Konstantin A|last2=Efimov|first2=Yaroslav O|date=2019-12-01|journal=International Journal of Offshore and Polar Engineering|issue=4|doi=10.17736/ijope.2019.jc768|volume=29|pages=400–407|issn=1053-5381|last3=Gudoshnikov|first3=Yury P|last4=Tarasov|first4=Petr A|last5=Chernov|first5=Alexey V|last6=Svistunov|first6=Ivan A|last7=Maksimova|first7=Polina V|last8=Buzin|first8=Igor  V|last9=Nesterov|first9=Alexander V}}</ref>

== 詞源 ==
冰山的英語{{lang|en|''Iceberg''}}是[[借譯|借譯]]自[[荷蘭語|荷蘭語]]的''ijsberg''，其字面上的意思是“冰山”<ref>Online Etymology Dictionary. ''[http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=iceberg&searchmode=none iceberg] {{Wayback|url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=iceberg&searchmode=none |date=20090409205001 }}''. URL accessed March 29, 2006.</ref>。''ijsberg'' [[同源詞|同源]]到[[丹麥語|丹麥語]]的{{lang|da|''Isbjerg''}}、[[德語|德語]]的{{lang|de|''Eisberg''}}、[[低地德語|低地德語]]的''Iesbarg''以及[[挪威語|挪威]]和[[瑞典語|瑞典語]]的''Isberg''。

== 概述 ==
[[File:Sunset_iceberg_2.jpg|thumb]]海面上的冰山]]
冰山多為[[純水|純水]]结冰形成。冰的密度約為917kg/m<sup>3</sup>，而海水的密度約為1025kg/m<sup>3</sup>，依照[[阿基米德定律|阿基-{米}-得定律]]我們可以知道，自由漂浮的冰山約有90%體積沉在海水表面下。因此看着浮在水面上的形状并猜不出水下的形状。這也是為何有'''冰山一角'''一說來形容嚴重的問題只顯露出表面的一小部分。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.sccscience.com/2008/11/today-in-1956-largest-iceberg-on-record.html |title=Largest Iceberg on Record |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2011-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110113175017/http://blog.sccscience.com/2008/11/today-in-1956-largest-iceberg-on-record.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.usatoday.com/weather/resources/coldscience/2005-01-20-1956-antarctic-iceberg_x.htm Antarctica shed a 208-mile-long berg in 1956] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/weather/resources/coldscience/2005-01-20-1956-antarctic-iceberg_x.htm |date=20110212053313 }}, originally reported in the ''Polar Times'', vol. 43, page 18.</ref>

== 分類 ==

=== 尺寸 ===
[[File:Carlb-newfoundland-iceberg-2002.jpg|thumb]]的冰山]]
目前國際上對於冰山的尺寸和大小分類的依據主要是使用{{tsl|en|International Ice Patrol|國際冰巡邏隊}}所設計的分類表：<ref name="iipfaq">[http://www.uscg.mil/LANTAREA/IIP/docs/VOOP.pdf Ice, Weather, and Sea Surface Temperature Reports] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uscg.mil/LANTAREA/IIP/docs/VOOP.pdf |date=20110608233625 }}, URL accessed January 14, 2009</ref>

