== 監測 ==
[[南极|南极]]、[[北極|北極]]、[[五大湖|五大湖]]和[[切薩皮克灣|切薩皮克灣]]一帶的冰情由美國{{tsl|en|National Ice Center|国家冰中心}}监测。目前唯一有組織編號的是南極一帶的冰山<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.physorg.com/news79026480.html |title=Alaskan storm cracks giant iceberg to pieces in faraway Antarctica |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605224459/http://www.physorg.com/news79026480.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有一边长于10[[英里|英里]]的冰山都有一个名字，用一个字母起头，加上排号数字。字母指定冰山来源的地区：<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xs4all.nl/~carlkop/ronne.html |title=NOAA October 15, 1998 - New Iceberg Breaks off Ronne Ice Shelf in Antarctica |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2010-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100823164811/http://www.xs4all.nl/~carlkop/ronne.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*'''A''' – 0°到[[西经|西经]]90°
*'''B''' –西经90°到180°
*'''C''' – [[东经|东经]]90°到180° 
*'''D''' – 0°到东经90°

